Definition: the civil and religious leader of a Muslim state considered to be a representative of Allah on earth
Example: many radical Muslims believe a Khalifah will unite all Islamic lands and people and subjugate the rest of the world
Synonyms: calif, kaliph, kalif, khalif, khalifah, ruler, Muslim, the, civil, and, religious, leader, of, a, state, considered, to, be, representative, Allah, on, earth, many, radical, Muslims, believe, Khalifah, will, unite, all, Islamic, lands, people, subjugate, rest, world
Category: noun.person
